%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Railways%3A%20NHSRCL%20Announces%20Job%20Openings%20For%20Managerial%20Roles%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20High%20Speed%20Rail%20Corporation%20Limited%20(NHSRCL)%20is%20inviting%20applications%20for%20the%20position%20of%20GM%20(finance)%2C%20AGM%20(finance)%20and%20general%20manager%20(O%20and%20M).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20appointment%20will%20be%20made%20on%20a%20deputation%20basis%20for%20a%20period%20of%20five%20years%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20chosen%20candidates%20will%20get%20a%20monthly%20salary%20on%20%E2%80%98parent%20pay%20plus%20deputation%20allowances%E2%80%99%20and%20perks%20as%20per%20company%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWho%20can%20apply%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20requirements%20for%20the%20posts%20are%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFor%20AGM%20(finance)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20candidate%20should%20have%20at%20least%20eight%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20finance%2C%20budgeting%20or%20accounting%20matters%20with%20respect%20to%20establishment%2C%20expenditure%2C%20bookkeeping%2C%20taxation%2C%20tender%20and%20contracts%2C%20project%20work%2C%20and%20audit%20internal%20checks.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Cp%3ECandidates%20aged%2050%20and%20below%20can%20apply%20for%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECandidates%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332017%2Findian-railways-rites-announces-job-openings-for-engineers-salary-eligibility%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ework%20experience%20in%20railway%20contracts%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20handling%20divisions%20for%20more%20than%20two%20years%20are%20preferred.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFor%20GM%20(finance)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20candidate%20should%20have%20at%20least%2010%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20finance%2C%20budgeting%20or%20accounting%20matters%20with%20respect%20to%20establishment%2C%20expenditure%2C%20bookkeeping%2C%20taxation%2C%20tender%20and%20contracts%2C%20project%20work%2C%20and%20audit%20internal%20checks.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Cp%3ECandidates%20aged%2055%20and%20below%20can%20apply%20for%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20desirable%20if%20the%20candidate%20has%20experience%20in%20railway%20contracts%20and%20handling%20divisions%20for%20more%20than%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Col%20start%3D%5C%223%5C%22%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFor%20general%20manager%20(O%20and%20M)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20applicant%20should%20have%20experience%20of%20at%20least%2010%20years%20in%20train%20operations%20and%20management-related%20works%20in%20railway%20PUs.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20candidate%20should%20be%20well%20versed%20in%20fidic%20conditions%20of%20the%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20apply%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EQualified%20applicants%20can%20download%20the%20official%20application%20format%2C%20complete%20it%2C%20and%20then%20submit%20the%20filled%20application%20form%20along%20with%20Vigilance%2FDAR%20Clearance%20and%20the%20APARS%20of%20the%20last%20five%20years%20of%20service%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F288054%2Fplaces-to-travel-in-indian-railways-magnificent-vistadome-coaches%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMinistry%20of%20Railways%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20they%20should%20send%20an%20advance%20copy%20of%20the%20filled%20application%2C%20signed%2C%20via%20email%20to%20mgrhr3dli%40nhsrcl.in%20before%20the%20specified%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20closing%20date%20for%20submitting%20the%20application%20form%20is%2030%20days%20from%20the%20date%20of%20publication%20of%20the%20advertisement%20%E2%80%94%2010%20October%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20further%20details%2C%20check%20t