.com%2F332112%2Fisro-chandrayaan-3-project-director-p-veeramuthuvel-gaganyaan-tamil-nadu%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%20Switches%20to%20Organic%20Farming%20After%20Losing%20Father%20to%20Cancer%2C%20Doubles%20Profit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERaised%20by%20her%20widowed%20mother%20with%20five%20other%20siblings%2C%20Rubi%20Pareek%20had%20a%20difficult%20childhood.%20At%20the%20very%20young%20age%20of%20one%2C%20she%20had%20lost%20her%20father%20to%20cancer.%20Often%2C%20the%20family%20would%20not%20have%20money%20to%20buy%20vegetables%20and%20would%20be%20left%20to%20depend%20on%20dry%20%3Cem%3Echapatis%20%3C%2Fem%3E(flatbreads)%20and%20chutneys.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20150%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%20%3C%2Fem%3Eland%20but%20our%20family%20had%20to%20sell%20most%20of%20our%20property%20and%20all%20our%20savings%20on%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20treatment.%20We%20were%20told%20that%20it%20was%20because%20of%20pesticide-laden%20vegetables%20that%20the%20risk%20of%20life-threatening%20diseases%20like%20cancer%20increased%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rubi%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20we%20struggled%20for%20even%20a%20penny.%20I%20am%20from%20a%20conservative%20society%20where%20women%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20step%20out%20of%20homes%20to%20work.%20So%2C%20my%20mother%20raised%20her%20five%20children%20with%20whatever%20savings%20we%20were%20left%20with%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2039-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20financial%20hardships%2C%20the%20Dausa%20resident%20could%20not%20study%20after%20class%2010.%20At%20the%20age%20of%2020%2C%20she%20was%20married%20into%20an%20agricultural%20family%20where%20she%20found%20a%20sense%20of%20empowerment.%20Not%20only%20this%2C%20she%20helped%20her%20family%20convert%20nearly%2026%20acres%20of%20land%20into%20a%20profitable%20organic%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3