.%20If%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20start%20living%20sustainably%20now%2C%20we%20will%20lose%20the%20amazing%20resources%20that%20nature%20has%20to%20offer.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696948290000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D331903%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alankrutha%20Chandra%20and%20her%20husband%20Meher%20Gundavarum%20decided%20to%20embrace%20a%20sustainable%20lifestyle.%20They%20quit%20their%20jobs%20and%20started%20'Elephant%20In%20You'%2C%20a%20Hyderabad-based%20brand%20that%20covers%20three%20essentials%20of%20living%20%E2%80%94%20food%2C%20clothing%20and%20shelter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98I%20Woke%20Up%20In%20The%20Hospital%E2%80%99%3A%20It%20Took%20Everything%20For%20Me%20to%20Fight%20Depression%20%26amp%3B%20Rebuild%20Myself%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20warning%3A%20Mention%20of%20suicide.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJaikishaan%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20start%20his%20venture%20DreamChair%20Club%20was%20driven%20in%20part%20by%20his%20personal%20journey%20of%20ups%20and%20downs.%20The%20foundation%20that%20helps%20people%20across%20the%20globe%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F308756%2Fmanila-bachan-recovery-journey-from-sexual-abuse-bipolar-disorder-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efind%20motivation%3C%2Fa%3E%20amidst%20testing%20times%20was%20born%20from%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20trying%20period%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%2038-year-old%E2%80%99s%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20mindset%20coach%20learnt%20early%20on%20how%20unpredictable%20life%20can%20be%20when%20his%20father%20%E2%80%94%20whose%20dream%20it%20was%20to%20see%20Jaikishaan%20p