ear%20before%20being%20posted.%20The%20final%20place%20of%20posting%20will%20be%20decided%20after%20the%20training%20is%20completed.%20They%20will%20be%20posted%20across%20the%20country%20and%20will%20have%20to%20work%20in%20shifts.%20Selected%20candidates%20will%20get%20a%20salary%20of%20Rs%2040%2C000-1%2C40%2C000%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWho%20can%20apply%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20official%20notification%2C%20there%20are%20495%20vacancies%20for%20engineers%20which%20includes%20120%20electrical%20engineers%2C%20200%20mechanical%20engineers%2C%2080%20electronics%2Finstrumentation%20engineers%2C%2065%20mining%20engineers%20and%2030%20civil%20engineers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3ECandidates%20should%20have%20a%20full%20time%20bachelors%20degree%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331340%2Fbits-pilani-engineer-couple-build-sustainable-house-without-cement-brick-rajasthan-architecture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eengineering%20or%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%2FAMIE%20with%20not%20less%20than%2065%20percent%20marks.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ECandidates%20are%20required%20to%20have%20appeared%20for%20the%20Graduate%20Aptitude%20Test%20in%20Engineering%20(GATE)%20for%20the%20year%202023%20and%20must%20have%20successfully%20qualified%20the%20examination.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EAge%20limit%20for%20unreserved%20candidates%20is%2027%20and%20reserved%20candidates%20as%20per%20government%20norms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20apply%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3ECandidates%20can%20apply%20online%20on%20careers.ntpc.co.in%20or%20visit%20careers%20section%20at%20www.ntpc.co.in%20with%20their%20GATE-2023%20registration%20number.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ECandidates%20belonging%20to%20General%2FEWS%2FOBC%20category%20are%20required%20to%20pay%20a%20non-refundable%20application